<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>500 — Internal Server Error | FounderPad</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { background: #0b1326; color: #dae2fd; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui; margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .headline { font-family: 'Manrope', system-ui; }
    .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
    .primary { color: #c0c1ff; }
    .muted { color: #c7c4d7; }
    .btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4648d4, #6063ee); color: white; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: transform 0.2s; }
    .btn:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
    .error-code { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono'; font-size: 120px; font-weight: 700; color: #c0c1ff; opacity: 0.1; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="position: relative; text-align: center; max-width: 500px; padding: 2rem;">
    <div class="error-code">500</div>
    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 64px; color: #c0c1ff; opacity: 0.6;">report_problem</span>
      <h1 class="headline" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;">Something broke.</h1>
      <p class="muted" style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Our systems hit an unexpected error. We've been notified and are looking into it.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 18px;">arrow_back</span>
        Back to Safety
      </a>
      <p class="mono" style="font-size: 11px; color: #464554; margin-top: 2rem;">ERROR_CODE: 500_INTERNAL // FOUNDERPAD</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
